Pakistan Observer published a 100-page special report on Feb 18 after a one and a half month open-ended survey in the South Asian country. About 84.3 percent of the respondents declared Xi as the "Role Model Statesman of the Year 2015".
"President Xi Jinping is a great leader with a vision and fresh ideas," the advisor to Pakistan Prime Minister on Foreign Affairs Sartaj Aziz said at the launching ceremony for the special report on Feb 18. "Pakistan China Economic Corridor (CPEC) will prove a milestone in the growing unique friendly relations between the two countries," he added.
